{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Spicy Bites - Flavorful Food</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #cc0000;\n            --secondary-color: #f2e6e6;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 15px 1.66%;\n            background-color: var(--light-text);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            padding: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 180px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .locations {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .locations h2 {\n            color: var(--light-text);\n        }\n\n        .location-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 45%;\n            margin: 15px 2.5%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .location-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .location-item p {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/cc0000/ffffff?text=Spicy+Bites+Flavor') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Spicy Bites</h1>\n        <p>Ignite Your Taste Buds!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a>\n        <a href=\"#locations\">Locations</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Experience the Heat!</h2>\n            <p>Authentic flavors that will leave you craving more.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section id=\"menu\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Signature Dishes</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/cc0000/ffffff?text=Spicy+Chicken\" alt=\"Spicy Chicken Dish\">\n                <h3>Inferno Chicken</h3>\n                <p>Our most popular dish! Tender chicken marinated in our secret spicy blend, grilled to perfection.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/cc0000/ffffff?text=Veggie+Curry\" alt=\"Vegetarian Curry Dish\">\n                <h3>Volcano Veggie Curry</h3>\n                <p>A vibrant medley of fresh vegetables simmered in a rich, fiery curry sauce.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/cc0000/ffffff?text=Spicy+Tacos\" alt=\"Spicy Tacos Dish\">\n                <h3>Dragon's Breath Tacos</h3>\n                <p>Three soft tacos filled with seasoned meat, topped with a fiery salsa and cooling crema.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"locations\" class=\"locations\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Find a Spicy Bites Near You</h2>\n            <div class=\"location-item\">\n                <h3>Downtown Metropolis</h3>\n                <p>123 Main Street, Metropolis, CA 90210</p>\n                <p>Phone: (555) 123-4567</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"location-item\">\n                <h3>Uptown Cityville</h3>\n                <p>456 Oak Avenue, Cityville, NY 10001</p>\n                <p>Phone: (555) 987-6543</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"location-item\">\n                <h3>Suburbia Townsville</h3>\n                <p>789 Pine Lane, Townsville, TX 75001</p>\n                <p>Phone: (555) 555-1212</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"location-item\">\n                <h3>Beachside Haven</h3>\n                <p>101 Ocean Drive, Haven, FL 33101</p>\n                <p>Phone: (555) 444-7878</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Spicy Bites</h2>\n            <p>Founded in 2010, Spicy Bites was born from a passion for bold flavors and a desire to share authentic, exciting dishes with the world. We use only the freshest ingredients and our time-tested recipes to bring you an unforgettable culinary experience. Whether you crave mild or wild, we've got something to set your taste buds alight!</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Spicy Bites. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for smooth scrolling (optional)\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}